Title: TCP/IP OVER ATM NETWORKS: SOME EXPERIENCES  
Author: Dejan Mircevski, 
Address: Houston, Texas, USA  
Affiliation: Department of Computer Science, Rice University,  
Abstract: This paper describes an AAL-5 and ATM protocol implementation that allows ATM networks to be used in an internet as Logical IP Subnetworks (LIS). The implemented protocols may be run either on real networking hardware or on a software simulator. 
